Class AdventureCardViewTUI

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.is25am22new.Client.View.TUI.AdventureCardViewTUI
public class AdventureCardViewTUI extends Object
Methods used to show the cards in the TUI the simple show method displays the info of the card as it is the InGame version displays the information necessary for the player to play the card
